      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.archetypes.XuveQGcwx7b60G1g]{Phrenic Adept}</p>\n<p>Your psychic abilities have grown strong enough to allow you to duplicate the effects of a few specific spells. Once per day, you can cast a spell from the following list as a spell-like ability: @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.spells.SysRFlYml1f1Eofd]{Charm Monster}, @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.spells.4Z6WeMM9uJ1U0wG6]{Clairaudience/Clairvoyance}, and @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.spells.OHGWvzUb9MJCNB8u]{Psychokinetic Strangulation}. At 13th level, you can use this ability twice per day, and at 17th level, you can use this ability three times per day. The save DC of these spells is equal to 10 + the spell level + your key ability score modifier.</p>"
